title: Are You A Victim?
itunes:title: Are You A Victim?
description:
Episode 565 -  Have you been playing the victim your whole life and not even known it? For most of my life, I played the victim. One thing I didn't realize was when I finally let go of playing the victim card, my life was fully 100% in my control and that is when I was able to turn my life into the life I have always wanted. In this episode I will teach you to do the same!
